                  </persName> were indicted for<rs id="t18381231-525-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18381231-525-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18381231-525-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> steal<lb></lb>ing, on the <rs id="t18381231-cd-90" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381231-525-offence-1 t18381231-cd-90"></join>24th of December</rs>, 35lbs. weight of flour, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18381231-name-604" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-604" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
